values:
is my last enrty for the year.
HORRRRRRAY!


So, Saturday was this Saturday.
It wasnt to wonderful.
BUUUT. Its the marker for the end of the yearrrr!
I am excited.

Our english class doesnt have to go.
Since we are ahead.

So i guess to clear up the confusion:
Not high school. but college.

Thank goodness.
We have next week off. 
Well, Wednesday and Friday.
I am going to need that break.
I neeed sleep.
Especially after this weekend. PROMMM!

This movie kinda makes me giggle.

"get bent tax man."
Ohh if only we could ALL say that.



annnd. Yum Yum food in class.

hehe.

I am surprised.
Dr. AC made the statement "Women are better than men"
and the boys in the class let that slide?!
WHAAAA?
Amazing.
You would thing of ALL things they would argue about, it would be that.

I love our class.
They make me giggle.
Although, i am sure that at some point during the rest of the year she is going to KILL us.
Straight up kill us.
Its okay Dr. AC, you know you LOOOOOOOVE us!
We entertain you. Right?

Of all days i actually read.
I was late.
Because we got pulled over.
Because we were speeding to get here.
Frisco cops are mean too.

Hmph.
Just my luck.

I definately think we should do this in our high school classes.
Since we all know when the teachers get their evaluation by the principals,
the teachers tell their classes to behave, and they are a MUCH better teacher.
If they actually got the opintion of the students, they would get a lot more honest evaluations.
And most of the teachers would no longer work there.

Was pretty much the death of me.
I actually feel worn out because of this paper.
I am so happy that it is OVER!
SO SO SO SO SO SO SO SO happy that i am done with that!
Writing this paper when i was pretty much dying made it muuuch worse.

I am definately understanding how Dr. AC was feeling the other day.
I do believe i have come down with the flu. Or something very similar.
I am sitting here trying to concentrate on my paper.
But i cant. all i can think about is how absolutly awful i feel.
I would much rather be sleeping. But this paper must get done.

I have counted that we have only ten more classes.
Thank goodness.
its not that i dont like this class, but its the thougth that college classes being over is one more step to graduation.
And i cant wait until graduation.

I wonder why so many people missed class today.
Only about half the class was there today.
I am not sure if they dropped or just decided to not come.
But thats okay, because we had our typical '"attendance quiz" that was just our name.
I love those quizes.
Two quizes today that i did quite well on.
Thank goodness.
Well, one was going to be a good grade no matter what.
But the quiz we had over the readings today wasnt bad at all.
I actually did quite well.

I fully planned on starting on my research paper this weekend.
But i think i might be wayyyy to dead to even think about it!
Considering i have to be up at 4am tomorrow.
All for a JROTC meet i am going to go watch.
I am going to be way to tired to even think of my book.
I will be lucky if i will be able to survive at work on Sunday, 
Let alone, use my brain for REAL work.

But if i choose not to go tomorrow, (which is a possiblility, since I might choose Sleep over the drill meet. :]])
I will start on my paper.

I completely forgot today was Friday the 13th.
But it was a pretty good morning. 
and it will be a even better day.

And on the discussion of slamming doors.
I used to slam doors, but not NEARLY as much anymore.
It gets me into EVEN MORE trouble.
When I am pissed I generally yell, ALOT.
and then cry.

Ahhh, and the infamous slamming the phone shut.
I do that constantly. 
And i have thrown it numerous times.
Especially this past week.
Which is why it is probably screwing up.


Annnd HORRRRRRRRAY for being done with Doll House.
which will give us time off in the end. 
:]]
Thank goodness.

It is quite hot in here.
Since I am quite burnt.
Like a lobster.


And i am quite amazed.
There isnt really that much Smart Ass-ness in todays class.
There is actually SERIOUS discussion going on.
Hm. Imagine that.

I am much to tired for class today.
Yesterday and Last night was the night from HELLL.
I have decided the NAVY sucks.

but that is besides the point.
I wish i could go this Friday, but i dont believe I can.
Sami and I have made plans to have a girls night.
Which is well needed after last night.

HEY! i can see if Sami wants to go.
She is a CCCC student. 
So, why not?
Does anyone know how many post and comments we need by the end of this semester?

Starbucks.
Yummy.
I actually feel much more awake today.
and i got less sleep than i usually do.
But the lovely caffeine of my Caramel Macchiatto is definitely kicking in.

Yummm Yummm Yummmm.
Love me some Starbucks.


So, no tranquilizers in my latte this morning Dr. AC!

I am so glad that our exam is over the unit of drama and film.
I feel more at home with drama. 
Theater helpes that one alot.

So, maybe theater wasnt ALL bad.

Why do teachers like to pile up all the projects at the same time?

I had the paper due today.
The research paper.
TWO government projects.
an Enteprenuership project.
i am going to have a french composition soon. 

And i am going to have to also balance work. 
and possibly another job. Since i only get like six hours a week.


I can so do this though. 



Mmmmmhm. Today's class is alot more calm than normal. Does anyone know why?
I bet Kayler does.

I suck at analytical papers.
and i will be the first one to admit it.
I think i have a good point, but it just ends up a summary.

This sucks.
:[[

That quiz wasnt too terribly bad.
I think i actually passed that one.
With the exception of the questions about Young Goodman Brown.



Hmmm, I want to ALMOST win the lottery.

I have decided to write my rewrite paper tomorrow or Thursday.
And I am going to bring it to the teacher i am a teacher's aid for and have her grade it.
If it is a B or below, i am going to have her tell me what i can to make an A.
Since i have figured it out. If it would be an A in high school, it would be a B(ish) in College.

I am writing like i was taught in my Pre Ap classes and such since 7th grade.
And that isnt what they are looking for in college classes.
They sit there and tell you that High School prepares you for college and such. 
But in my true opinion, it messes you up.
College is much more open minded. You can have an opinion.
When in high school, they want your opinion to be YOUR opinion.


Blah. i am getting off on a tangent.

But i am determined to make this paper a billion times better.

Damn it.
I have to do a manditory rewrite.
I thought i actually did pretty good when i was writing it.
But clearly i didnt.
I think i am going to write my paper in Teacher Aid this week.
That way, if i have any questions, i can ask Mrs. Jackson. 
I can do this. Better. I hope.

Haha. My father has never actually said to a guy i was dating "I know what your intentions are." But he has threatened.
He actually threatened to do that with Dallas. DUN DUN DUN.
I am scared for him. Haha.

Woooow. This class is interesting.
I love when we have discussions like this one.
People make the funniest comments in this class.

I plan to have my paper written in Teacher Aid. 
That would be nice. To have it done early.


HORRAY FOR TEACHER AID.

And maybe that way she can help me. 
Since she is an English teacher.


Annnnd i am having a freaking coughing attack in class. This sucks.
I cant seem to go more than like thirty seconds with out coughing.

Blah.

Alright. The papers are getting longer.
And i have issues with making the papers long enough.
They always seem to be a half page, or page, too short.
Darn. This sucks.
Soooo, i get to go home this afternoon and figure out some way to make it longer, oh, and maybe better.
But i dont mind, because now, i dont have to go over to "the guys" house. and i can avoid awkward moments.
Horray.

Paper numero dos is going to suuuuuuck.

I have been sitting here trying to start it for...ohhhh....about.....two or three hours.

I really am not sure what we are supposed to do.

Like i KINDA understand, but not fully.

And i didnt think Friday would come up so quickly.

like today Kayler and I were in class and we started talking about the paper. and Kayler said something about getting it done.
I simply looked at her and said "What, its not due until Friday" 
I really didnt think it was Thursday.

I have gone to school for only two days.

Monday was a Teacher Work Day.
And Tuesday was TAKS.



GAHHH! im so screwed.

Oh my. 
That quiz was awful.

I am wayyyy to icky today to be able to do that.
I woke up and felt like death.
I think I am getting siiiick.

It is going to be difficult to pay attention today.
My brain feels like they are going to explode.

I just recently dropped one guy, and am interested in another. 
All of this 5 days before V-day. 

Maybe i should take out an add like we read in class. 
"Are YOU the one?!" 
"I like long walks on the beach and  Blah blah blah blah"




Bahhhh, i dont want to talk about the book review. 
Ew. I have to start reading the book. 
Yeahh, i dont even have the book yet. 
Yes, i admit it. I am procrastinating.

Oh, wow.

I actually did pretty good on paper 1A.
I got a 91.
I thought i did HORRRRRRRIBLE on that paper.
But i always think i do horrible on the papers.
But i guess i did better than i had originally thought.

Yeahh, that quiz was HORRIBLE.
I know i failed that.
Actually, there is no way i passed that. considering i only answered two questions.
But i do know i did get the two i actually answered right. Well, i think. I hope.

So, i am pretty sure that last paper of mine was not the greatest.


First it was over Big Fish and i hate that book. no not hate. loaht.

And i wrote the paper when i was quite angy at someone. 
and i edited it on a day that i couldnt concentrate if my life depended on it.


I had like major ADD that day. Yesterday right?
Yeahh, yesterday.

LIke in French. I had a test. I couldnt concentrate AT ALL. We had an oral part, and she kept talking and asking the question.
I would think of the answer and it would jump out of my head.


Annnd earlier in Englis our group kinda kept getting distracted. and Martin decided to tell on us. :[[
and Kayler told him to turn around all sarcastically. and he thought she was serious.

But we couldnt keep on track then either. it was difficult!



I think it might be this week. becasue right now my brain is jumping allll over the place.



And my house is quite cold.

Trying to convine Dr. AC to change the time that papers are due.

Hmm, is it just me, or are the ones that are fussing about the due time are the same ones that were fussing about the Livejornal. 

Its not that bad. i like the 5pm, becasue if it was midnight, i wouldnt do it. i would get distracted. and forget to do it.

Horray for the last essay over Big Fish. Ever.

I have come to loath this novel.

The first time i read it i just disliked it. 

I now LOATH it.


*"What Is This Feeling" from the musical Wicked pops into mind*

"What is this feeling?
Fervid as a flame,
Does it have a name?
Yes!:Loathing
Unadulterated loathing" 



I have never in my life been so excited about writing a paper. but i am since this is the LAST Big Fish paper....EVVVVVVVVVVER.

I actually did my paper.

I actually feel i did a pretty good job on this paper.

But i go to turn it in at 4:59.

But then my computer decides to be gay and slow down.

So, i try to turn it in at 5 on the dot, but noooo, it wont let me.

go figure.

Life Hates Me. Alot.

I think i might go cry now.

I have tonight to write the first paper.
I do realize this is just a summary.
and it only needs to be like two pages.
I most likely wont have an issue actually writing the paper,
my issue will be to START the paper. 
Lately i have been having the issue with putting thigs off.
For example, rereading Big Fish.
I put that off, but somehow seemed to still make good grades on the two quizes.
Luckly i actually read it the first time. (i kinda skimmed the first half, and actually put effort into reading the second half)

My goal is to do AMAZING this semester, rather than medeoker.
 
i made a B the first time around, so i can definately make an A this semester.
Right?!

Everyone is complaining about the online journals.

Its really not that bad.

Its better than half the things she could give us.

Its better than the things they would be giving us in the High School classes.

She gives us more "freedoms" than the high school teachers would.

Lets stop complaining about this journal. Its REALLY NOT THAT BAD. Its an easy grade!

I am not wanting to be here this morning.
I need Starbucks. 
Buuut, i cant have Starbucks.
I gave up Starbucks.
It was HELL getting up this morning. Considering i have not gone to bed before 2 am this whole weekend.

Actually, i dont think i have gotten good sleep in WEEKS!


I.Want.Starbucks.
I.Need.Starbucks.
I.Miss.My.Starbucks.

Ah! i can survive this class and government without Starbucks. Right?!

Wow. Today can definately go on my list of Worst Days Ever.

It started out with an interesting Government class. 

Then after school, a nice little event happened. (An event that i am not going to go into) Resulting in me BALLING. and Terrified.

Then Kayler and i almost die on the way home from Coldstone. All thanks to some really drunk guys. Or atleast thats how it seemed with the way they were driving. (i.e Almost driving into the median....Head on.)

Then i come home, and read something someone had posted on their myspace. Yes, i do realize i am talking about something someone posted...On MYSPACE....but, this is not the first time this has happened. 

It said something to the fact that she hates a certian song (lips of an angel) because of a certian "BLONDE WHORE"
and that there are two people that she would like to punch in the nose...those two people jsut happened "to be best friends".

Yes, i realize that that isnt that specific. but i know. i know thats about me. its not the first time i have had issues with her. She threatened to kick my ass at the HOMECOMING GAME because i was "taking shit" about her and her boyfriend.

Her. no. but the boyfriend. Yes. i mean he was my ex. he broke up with me and INSTANTLY started dating her. Even when he told me he "loved me" and "would always love me" and "wouldnt want to hurt me. ever again." That was screwed up. But that whole situation is besides the point and old news.


Buuut as you all know how that song goes. A guy has a girlfriend, and his ex girl or lover or whatever calls him....ect, ect. You know the song.

 
and i know she thinks I still have a problem with him and her dating. Buuuut i dont, i got hurt by him WAYYY to much. and im over it. i moved on. and i am pretty sure he moved on. now she just needs to move on.  I dont want to be with him. In fact,  I am glad she came around. because if she hadnt. i can almost guarantee that him and i would still be in a relationship. Miserable.



I am so tired of High School drama. I am ready for college.

LIFE HERE I COME! WILLING TO DO ANYTHING TO GET OUT OF THIS DRAMA FILLED HELL HOLE! I AM READY FOR LIFE!


(finally, I am not deathly scared of life and the future)

So, I'm sitting here doing my project for Government. 

My group's topic is "Anti Government Symbolic Speech Protest"

We have to discuss the symbolism of burning the American flag.

While researching for the subject i came across a web page that had "Flag Code" or the acceptable rules when it comes to the American Flag.

It stated that it is not acceptable to "wear the flag as wearing apparel"," It should never be carried flat or horizontally, but always aloft and free." and many other things. like you arent supposed to make a flag into a cake because you cut it up and eat it and such.

Its amazing the things we have rules about.





And on that note. I am realllllly reallly not looking forward to English class tomorrow. i havent even opened my Big Fish book this semester. Yes, i admit it, i didnt actually read the first 90 pages, i somehow remembered all of it from last semester. I realize thats not a good thing, and i should actually be reading it. But hey, i still made a 100 on that quiz. I even knew the giants name was Karl. :]]

and i dont look forward to reading the other half. which i should actually read since, i kinda stopped paying attention to what i was reading. 

Yeahh, thats what i will be doing tonight. Reading Big Fish. I might need some Starbucks before starting to read. Because with the way i have been sleeping, reading the most exciting novel could put me to sleep, let alone a book i have already read. And i wasnt to fond of it the first time around either.

I REALLLY REALLY REALLLY do not want to read Big Fish again. The first time really wasnt all that bad. But i dont want to read it again. atleast not all within the same school year. I have to wait forever to reread books. The repition is not fun. But i figure i will have to suck it up if i want to do good in this class this semester.

We are now back in Dr. AC's English class. Which means: more early mornings and sleep deprived children.
Wow. I now rememeber why i got Starbucks every single morning. 

I am addicted, which is why i wrote my "addiction paper" on Starbucks.

Kayler and i told ourselves that we would cut down on our Starbucks intake. Considering that we spend around $100 a month just for Starbucks.


But, i reallllllllly don't know if I can make it through the year with lack of caffine.

Yep. so i realize that no one reads or updates these things. That is a good thing at the moment.

I am so so so so SOOOOO frustrated.

I have decided i give up on having a love life. Simply because i always seem to be screwed over by guys.

It happened YET AGAIN. last night. Third time in almost 4 months.

Daniel decides to tell me that he still loves his Ex, that he told me he was over.
and he doesnt know what to do. 

He wants me to help him decide. HOW THE HELL CAN I HELP HIM DECIDE THAT. 

All i told him was that i understand and that i have been there, then he asked me waht i did, and i told him that i moved on. 

I really dont know what to do.

I decided to leave the very last post for class today, since you know, This is where it started, this is where it will end. So, no i didnt forget to update it one last time.

This was a difficult thing to do.


Thank goodness its done.

I am less nervous about this paper now. 

But the thing is, i cant sleep. 


So i am worried that tomorrows class is going to come around and i am going to be warn out.

Gah. i hope that isnt the case.
